{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"MediaKeys.setServerCertificate()","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaKeys/setServerCertificate","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaKeys\"><code>MediaKeys</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methods</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaKeys/createSession\"><code>createSession()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><em><code>setServerCertificate()</code></em></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>This is an <a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Guidelines/Conventions_definitions#experimental\">experimental technology</a></strong><br>Check the <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">Browser compatibility table</a> carefully before using this in production.</p></div>\n<p>\n  The <strong><code>MediaKeys.setServerCertificate()</code></strong> method provides a\n  server certificate to be used to encrypt messages to the license server.\n</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token function\">setServerCertificate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>serverCertificate<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"Parameters","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"servercertificate\"><code>serverCertificate</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>An <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer\"><code>ArrayBuffer</code></a>, a <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/TypedArray\"><code>TypedArray</code></a>, or a <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/DataView\"><code>DataView</code></a> object containing the server certificate. The contents are Key System-specific. It MUST NOT contain executable code.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"return_value","title":"Return value","isH3":true,"content":"<p>A <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Promise\"><code>Promise</code></a> that resolves to a boolean. If the Key System implementation represented by this object's cdm implementation value does not support server certificates, return a promise resolved with false.</p>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/encrypted-media/#dom-mediakeys-setservercertificate","title":"Encrypted Media Extensions"}],"query":"api.MediaKeys.setServerCertificate"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.MediaKeys.setServerCertificate","dataURL":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaKeys/setServerCertificate/bcd.json"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"}],"summary":"The MediaKeys.setServerCertificate() method provides a\n  server certificate to be used to encrypt messages to the license server.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-06-15T16:40:35.000Z","source":{"folder":"en-us/web/api/mediakeys/setservercertificate","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/style/old/files/en-us/web/api/mediakeys/setservercertificate/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/9e3fbb4ff05782b2d988a8becc84a63a57a9be58","filename":"index.md"},"par